c: 14
v: 22
t: A devil say judgment issued GOD promised ona truthful promise ja promised ona ja lamat moj promise Ja had power ona; ja len invited ona ona accepted moj invitation! Therefore nie blame mi blame len yourselves! Moj complaining nie pomoc ona nor mozem tvoj complaining pomoc mna. Ja disbelieved tvoj idolizing mna! transgressors incurred painful retribution